{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_14_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 どっかーーーーん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の仕事終わり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ラジオ企画の資料作りに随分時間を取られてしまった\n今日くらいは早く帰るつもりだったんだが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツマカロンパーティーだよぉぉぉぉ！！\nウゥゥン……ウニャアアアアアァッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9566.6666667,
          "startTime": 25.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ！？　なんでアイドル事務所に奇声が！？\nダンススタジオの方から聞こえてきたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 26.983333842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "しっくりこないなー。あそこで叫んでた人は\n迫力満点だったし、もう少し大声で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4044880248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まさかあの声の正体が芽衣だったなんて……\nお、おい、芽衣、何をしてるんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7017548444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ウニャャアアアッ！？　{user}さん！？\nまだお仕事してたんだね、びっくりしたよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも今の叫び声はいい感じだったかも！\nありがとう、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして……じゃなくて、こんな遅くに\nなぜ叫んでるんだ。廊下にまで響いていたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの！？　うーん、公園で声を出してたんだけど\nさすがに近所迷惑だーって思ってここに来たんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもなぜ声を出す必要が……\nもしや最近の仕事で嫌なことでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うよー！　心配してくれるのは嬉しいけど\n芽衣はとっても元気だよー！　今のはねー、地下――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5666671753,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11753.332824699995,
          "startTime": 98.32
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "わっ、危ない危ない。あ～！　もうこんな時間だ～！\n沙季ちゃんが心配しちゃう！　帰らなきゃ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、はぐらかされてしまったな\n何か隠しているようだが。そういえばこの前も――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日前の帰り道",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.5666727702
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.5666727702
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.7000061035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　芽衣と怜と、葵……それに千紗？）\n（もう夜も更けてきたのに公園で何をしてるんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.3664302789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "葵ちゃんがくれたサングラス、最高だね～！\nどうかな？　芽衣って分からないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんもダークでクールでいい感じだよー！\nふふふ、芽衣達も早く出たいね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.6333272298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんの方も順調なんだね、助かるよー\n芽衣もノートにアイデア、沢山まとめてきたよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0999938965,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.333333299993,
          "startTime": 146.1333272298
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.0000213623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん、何を話してるんだ？　よく聞こえないな）\n（しかも、なんで夜にサングラスなんて掛けてるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.3000213623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、あそこにいるの{user}さんだよね\nねぇねぇ、芽衣達の変装、通じるか試して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13533.333333299994,
          "startTime": 170.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.6333536784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ？　うーん、そっか、内緒だもんね\n分かったよ。それじゃあ、一度解散ね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.2000233968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（しまった、じろじろ見過ぎたか）\n（でもあんな蜘蛛の子を散らすように逃げなくても……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 179.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "思い返せば、あの時から様子がおかしかったな\nし、心配だ。大丈夫か、芽衣……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 191.099995931
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 191.099995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、ブラッディドロドロドーナツにしてやる～\nん～……そんなの食べたくないし、なしだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "いつもと雰囲気を変えるなら、もっと怖い方がいいよね\n千紗ちゃんが見せてくれた映画みたいに……",
